<div class="prize-fellowship-recipient__body prize-fellowship-recipient__body--default field field-paragraph--field-body field-name-field-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><p>Arda Collins is a candidate in the Ph.D. program in poetry at the University of Denver. She holds an M.F.A. from the University of Iowa Writers' Workshop, where she was a Glenn Schaeffer Fellow. Her poems have been published in&nbsp;<em>The New Yorker</em>,&nbsp;<em>A Public Space</em>,&nbsp;<em>The American Poetry Review</em>&nbsp;and elsewhere. Her collection of poems,&nbsp;<em>It Is Daylight</em>&nbsp;won the 2008 Yale Series of Younger Poets Award, and is forthcoming from Yale University Press.</p>
